<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.9">
<l>taḷaiyaviḻu naṟuṅkuñcit tayarataṉṟaṉ kulamatalāy</l>
<l>vaḷaiyavoru cilaiyataṉāl matiḷilaṅkai yaḻittavaṉē</l>
<l>kaḷaikaḻunīr maruṅkalaruṅ kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>yiḷaiyavarkaṭ karuḷuṭaiyā yirākavaṉē tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Support of the lineage of Daśaratha</l>
<l rend="indent">with fragrant tufts of hair, the fastening of which becomes loosened!</l>
<l>O You who destroyed the fortressed Laṅkā with a unique bow, for [it] to bend!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">where the purple waterlilies that were weeded out blossom on the side!</l>
<l>O Rāghava who has grace for the younger brothers! Tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
